T imaging\nwith $0.09\"$when a power-law mass distribution for the lens system is adopted.\nOur PSF reconstruction technique is generic and applicable to data sets that\nhave multiple nearby point sources, enabling scientific studies that require\nhigh-precision models of the PSF.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jan 2016 21:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 14 Aug 2016 08:18:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-24"}
