ions of the observed clustering on encounter rates and mating success\nare discussed\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2016 08:10:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2016 07:39:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-27"}
