ding that a realistic amount of positive\ncorrelation in inter-event times only slightly affects the epidemic dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2016 11:21:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Aug 2016 13:11:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2020 05:11:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-20"}
